channel.title: Dusk tears - early morning mist (toveii remix) • [ambient]
channel.description:
My first remix post! My original plan was to make it lofi hiphop, and I didn’t it like as much. So, after couple of months, I got back into it. I gotta say though, the feeling of finishing and releasing a track is the best thing ever lol. Anyways, hope you all enjoy! Any feedback is appreciated!
